OL,5,G1310 Nations Championship
OL,6,     FFiji v Scotland (Kick-off 2.10pm).
OL,7,     FLauren Salter presents all the
OL,8,     Faction from the round-robin match
OL,9,     Fat Scottish Gas Murrayfield. While
OL,10,     FFiji are the designated hosts, the
OL,11,     Ffixture is being played here
OL,12,     Fbecause their main stadium does
OL,13,     Fnot meet the competition
OL,14,     Frequirements, and the Scots will
OL,15,     Fbe looking to avenge a 29-14
OL,16,     Fdefeat in Suva last November. With
OL,17,     Fanalysis from Greig Laidlaw and
OL,18,     FJohn Barclay, and commentary by
OL,19,     FMiles Harrison, Johnnie Beattie
OL,20,     Fand Ben Kay
